Tongues of Ex-Girlfriends(rich variety and reality)前女友们的舌头

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

This is the work that I have put the most effort into, with a very rich and varied tongue stretching action. It took almost three months from preparation to training. In the future, I will consider continuing to train the iterative version to increase the weight of this EMB, in order to cooperate with some poorly trained or poorly generalized characters EMB or Lora and also be able to stick out their tongues well.

这是我花费精力最多的一个作品，具有非常丰富多变细节的伸舌头动作。从准备到训练花费了几乎3个月的时间。后续会考虑继续训练迭代版本来增加该EMB的权重，以达到和某些训练不好或泛化差的人物emb或lora配合也能伸好舌头。

About Teeth version

Advantages: Strong expression and tension, fully demonstrating what it means to stick out your tongue with all your might.

Disadvantages: There is a lot of white feature vector pollution, and when partnering with non white female characters EMB/Lora, excellent prompt skills are required to ensure that the characters faithfully retain their faces while also being able to control their tongue extension.

Even if it is paired with the white female character EMB/Lora, it is necessary to be careful with prompts, otherwise it will also affect facial restoration.

will update a version in the future, which will keep the character's EMB face faithful(especially valuable for non white women emb)

优点：表现力和张力十足，充分展示了什么叫拼尽全力的伸舌头。

缺点：有较多的白人特征向量污染，在和非白人女性角色EMB/lora搭档时，需要高超的提示技巧才能让角色忠诚的保留脸部的同时又能驾驭伸舌头。

哪怕是和白人女性角色EMB/lora配合，也需要小心提示，不然也会影响脸部还原。

后续会更新一个版本，忠诚保留角色emb脸部的版本（对非白人女性emb特别有价值）

boring_e621 Negative Embedding

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

This is a download site for the negative embedding boring_e621. Its original huggingface repository, which goes into more detail about how it was trained and what it does, can be found here.

Briefly, This embedding attempts to capture what it means for an image to be uninteresting. So if you're using the Automatic1111 Stable Diffusion WebUI, you can place this file in stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings and add "by boring_e621" to your NEGATIVE prompt, and your results should be more interesting.

The title image for this model illustrates the quality improvements it can make to four simple prompts in the base SD 1.5 model.

Boring_e621 has been specifically reported to work well with the suggested models below.

Ethereal Girl

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

One of my first embeddings form a while back. Someone asked for a link, so here it is. It uses way to many tokens, but since I don't have the training images anymore, there isn't much I can do about that.

I made it using other generations I'd done. IIRC Jenna Ortega/Wednesday was the primary subject I was prompting for so the outputs tend to take a strong resemblance to her.

I might've used someone else's lora/embedding in the making of those generations but I couldn't tell you what they were at this point. (Think Ghostly Diffusion might've been one: https://civitai.com/models/5000/ghostly-diffusion)

I recommend negative "bloodshot eyes" and positive "detailed eyes" because the embedding will try its hardest to muddy them up.

Kisaragi Reona TI

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

The character from the not so popular Full Dive RPG anime. Very open ended model. Keeps the character, but will follow the prompts much closer with little need for weight adjustments. Works great at almost any step and scale config, compatible with most LoRAs and other embeddings.

To get the in-game outfit consistently, just type "fairy" into the prompt. Might also want to try adding "wings, thigh highs, gauntlets" for a closest match.

All training images were taken from r34, squared in paint3d, rescaled to 512x512 in birme, and then upscaled x4 in SD using R-ESRGAN. Trained at a rate of .0005 for 5k steps, but best result was around 3500-4200.
